--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
gCoder
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

A gedit plugin that provides extra functionality for coders.

Current:
 - _ and = are considered word characters when moving left/right word
 - comment selection
 - cut/copy current line if no selection
 - select current line (Ctrl + Shift + A)
 - scroll view up/down by one line (Ctrl + Up/Down)
 - previous document (Ctrl + Shift + Tab)
 - next document (Ctrl + Tab)
 - change selection case: upper (Ctrl + U), lower (Ctrl + L), capitalise, sentence, invert

Planned:
 - pair completion for (){}[]"'
 - bookmarks
 - base64 encode/decode
 - hash selection
 - lorem ipsum
 - find/replace with regex and file support


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Extract files to gedit plugins directory.

Single User : ~/.local/share/gedit/plugins

All Users   : /usr/share/gedit/plugins

